Job Category
Application Bid (in U.S. dollars) - Annual salary for a job/total fee for a gig. This can differ from the estimated salary/budget set out by the employer/client
Application Information - Tell the employer/client (and recommenders) why you are uniquely qualified to get this job/gig. Add any other details that would be helpful for the employer/client and recommenders (e.g., exactly what you would do on this job/gig). The more detail, the better. You can also explain why your bid is a higher or lower salary/fee than that set out by the employer/client.
You can only submit one application for a job. Your application will be publicly viewable on the marketplace. Make sure your information is correct before clicking Submit.
